{"_id":"GcTidY4mOWo8a0zb","name":"Soul Link","type":"feat","img":"icons/magic/life/heart-cross-strong-flame-green.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>At 11th level, the connection with your bound souls allows you to siphon their life force. As an action, choose an ally that you can see within 60 feet, including yourself. Then choose one of your bound souls. The target is healed by a number of hp equal to ten times the souls’ CR. The soul’s max hp is reduced by the same amount. Reducing its’ max hp to 0 in this way exorcises the soul.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"GUN pg. 9","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":60,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"heal","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Gunwitch 11","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"AxztLwp4myvb8Gpx":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"KwUZltXLYhrS7ZcD","name":"Expunge / Obliterate","type":"feat","img":"icons/skills/ranged/rocket-skull-fire-blue.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>At 7th level, you gain the ability to empower your abilities by sacrificing souls. On failing an attack roll, ability check, or saving throw, you can choose to exorcise a number of your bound souls. For each soul you sacrifice, add triple their CR to the failed roll, potentially changing it to a success.</p>\n<p>Additionally, on succeeding with an attack roll, you can choose to exorcise a number of your bound souls. For each soul you sacrifice, the attack deals additional d8 force damage equal to triple the souls’ CR, rounded down.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"GUN pg. 9","activation":{"type":"special","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Gunwitch 7","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"AxztLwp4myvb8Gpx":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"QXOKJIIrzoHwq6Fy","name":"Catastrophic Exhumation","type":"feat","img":"icons/magic/fire/explosion-flame-blue.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>At 15th level, once per long rest you can choose to use an action to exorcise all of your souls in one devestating blast. Choose a point within range of your Wicked Artifice. An explosion occurs at its’ center. Any creatures caught within a 50 foot radius of this point must attempt a Constitution saving throw. On a failed save, they take d6 force damage equal to four times the spent souls’ total CR and suffer an effect from the list below based on the type of the highest CR soul used. On a successful save, this damage is halved and they do not suffer the effect.</p>\n<p>Additionally, the area is considered difficult terrain for a number of minutes equal to the total CR of the spent souls.</p>\n<p>A creature effected by this ability makes another Constitution saving throw at the end of each of its turns. On a successful save, it no longer suffers the effect.</p>\n<table style=\"width:99.8513%;height:101.8px\" border=\"1\">\n<thead>\n<tr style=\"border-style:hidden;height:16.8px\">\n<td style=\"border-style:hidden;width:50.867%;height:16.8px\">Type</td>\n<td style=\"border-style:hidden;width:49.1361%;height:16.8px\">Effect</td>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height:17.3px\">\n<td style=\"width:50.867%;border-style:hidden;height:17.3px\">Aberration, Fey, Fiend</td>\n<td style=\"width:49.1361%;height:17.3px;border-style:hidden\">Charmed</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height:17.3px\">\n<td style=\"width:50.867%;height:17.3px;border-style:hidden\">Beast, Dragon, Undead</td>\n<td style=\"width:49.1361%;height:17.3px\">Frightened</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height:16.8px\">\n<td style=\"width:50.867%;height:16.8px;border-style:none\">Celestial, Elemental</td>\n<td style=\"width:49.1361%;height:16.8px;border-style:hidden\">Blinded</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height:16.8px\">\n<td style=\"width:50.867%;height:16.8px;border-style:hidden\">Construct, Giant</td>\n<td style=\"width:49.1361%;height:16.8px\">Paralyzed</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height:16.8px\">\n<td style=\"width:50.867%;height:16.8px;border-style:hidden\">Monstrosity, Ooze</td>\n<td style=\"width:49.1361%;height:16.8px;border-style:hidden\">Poisoned</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"GUN pg. 9","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":50,"width":null,"units":"ft","type":"radius"},"range":{"value":120,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"wis","actionType":"save","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"con","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Gunwitch 15","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"AxztLwp4myvb8Gpx":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"UfcekqH1jjru5KhQ","name":"Haunt","type":"feat","img":"icons/creatures/unholy/demon-fanged-horned-yellow.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>At 3rd level, you can use an action to bind your souls to a surface or object spanning an area no larger than 10 feet in diameter, effectively removing them as one of your bound souls. When you do, choose from the effects below. The effect remains active for a number of hours equal to your proficiency bonus, after which it is lost.</p>\n<p><em>Spook. </em>The soul acts as your proxy, allowing you to use an action to see and hear its surroundings using its senses for one minute. You can do so a number of times equal to triple the soul's CR.</p>\n<p><em><span style=\"white-space:pre\">Trap. </span></em>The soul is charged with destructive energy on binding. Once set, you can use an action to remotely detonate it. Anything within a 20 foot radius from the center of the trapped surface or object must make a Dexterity saving throw against your spell save DC. On a failure, they take a number of d8 necrotic damage equal to triple the souls’ CR, rounded down.</p>\n<p><em><span style=\"white-space:pre\">Teleport. </span></em>The soul acts as a portal, allowing you to use an action to transport yourself to it. You immediately appear within 5 feet of the location or object the soul is bound to. This effect remains active over a number of miles equal to the CR of the bound soul.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"GUN pg. 9","activation":{"type":"special","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Gunwitch 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"AxztLwp4myvb8Gpx":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"wGwEg1yWfXN2m9Di","name":"Soul Eater","type":"subclass","img":"icons/magic/unholy/strike-body-life-soul-green.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>Soul Eater gunwitches, generally, have a mostly utilitarian view of the souls they bind. For them, a soul is a malleable thing, ammunition to be spent. In spending it, the gunwitch ensures that their well never runs dry.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"GUN pg. 9","identifier":"soul-eater","classIdentifier":"gunwitch","advancement":[{"_id":"6ixwh7qmnenmu6d0","type":"ItemGrant","configuration":{"items":["Item.UfcekqH1jjru5KhQ"],"optional":false},"value":{},"level":3,"title":"Features","icon":""},{"_id":"vgqwu1tygvt6tvrm","type":"ItemGrant","configuration":{"items":["Item.KwUZltXLYhrS7ZcD"],"optional":false},"value":{},"level":7,"title":"Features","icon":""},{"_id":"3ewtvbraps9j4ixw","type":"ItemGrant","configuration":{"items":["Item.GcTidY4mOWo8a0zb"],"optional":false},"value":{},"level":11,"title":"Features","icon":""},{"_id":"sqamxiiv7xdbhnwm","type":"ItemGrant","configuration":{"items":["Item.QXOKJIIrzoHwq6Fy"],"optional":false},"value":{},"level":15,"title":"Features","icon":""}],"spellcasting":{"progression":"none","ability":""}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"AxztLwp4myvb8Gpx":3},"flags":{}}
